{"tid":1768830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李嘉誠基金會透過Google雲端AI技術，三星期處理逾4.3萬「應急錢」申請","createTime":"2019-12-04T10:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T19:09:34.000Z","uid":171506,"like":170,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"409ab052f4bd07a41aad84d503c8baf32bf62793","tid":1768830,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/476256?fbclid=IwAR3H4h0mmyokHL_8WHx1dyN9OusDbKc8VuVr4oJydr01tVyBhU96ejPVTEk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F476256%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3H4h0mmyokHL_8WHx1dyN9OusDbKc8VuVr4oJydr01tVyBhU96ejPVTEk&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=32c6410f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/476256?fbclid=IwAR3H4h0mmyokHL_8WHx1dyN9OusDbKc8VuVr4oJydr01tVyBhU96ejPVTEk</a><br />\n長和系創辦人李嘉誠旗下基金會，早前推出10億元「應急錢」計劃，向合資格中小企發放資助，計劃接獲4.3萬宗申請。基金會在計劃中以Google雲端人工智能（AI）技術，加速有關申請處理程序，整個申請和審核過程只需要數日便能完成，讓基金會能及時向合資格中小企發放資助。<br />\n基金會利用Google雲端Vision AI自動偵測、摘錄和分析圖像中的相關文字，光學字符識別技術（optical character reader，簡稱OCR）會準確地自動輸入所辦識的相關資料，節省了大量處理和核對申請資料的時間。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle雲端香港主管Lucy Werner表對於能與李嘉誠基金會合作感鼓舞，指Google雲端 Vision AI只需5秒時間就能辨識每個圖像中的相關文字，而60%的「應急錢」申請是透過手機或流動裝置提交，平均每宗申請會在8分鐘內完成提交，所以基金會僅需三星期便能處理逾4.3萬宗申請。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠基金會發言人張景如稱，與Google雲端合作展示了科技力量如何令中小企受惠；，而負責建立申請網站的生活易行政總裁馬宗傑則指，一般情況下，要建立這類型技術項目需要至少數週時間，但Google雲端專業團隊成功在短短三日內便把Cloud Vision AI應用整合到「應急錢」計劃中。<br />\n<br />\n「應急錢」計劃於10月29日宣布推出，整個申請平台在14日便建立了起來，所有資助會在本月中前分批送到成功申請者手中。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\nText by FORTUNE INSIGHT"},{"pid":"996232c32f825b523436341cf2852225954b1f8e","tid":1768830,"uid":71253,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"派錢都型過政府幾千倍"},{"pid":"00e176d58b96aec8aab26671dd0695c126718b54","tid":1768830,"uid":2607,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"影子政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9e149a0358916988c709fc08b068c873673469","tid":1768830,"uid":5490,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"香港政府重停留係寄實體表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bcaf31b3439457199a264c8443d3b0794a7dc2","tid":1768830,"uid":156542,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"地下嘅秩序 係誠哥管"},{"pid":"0b11ecf7b5f10463664943d3a4b26dbccee1f758","tid":1768830,"uid":250721,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"再次證明創科局有幾垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf377829d1dedaa509758b8c27939021149a8d2","tid":1768830,"uid":60449,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"你咁樣政府好無面喎<br />\n人地派6000千都派左成年 <br />\n仲要人手寫form 對form<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d148071dcfe1ab5d6566640d3f320b39f420b516","tid":1768830,"uid":59363,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"6e9e149a0358916988c709fc08b068c873673469","tid":1768830,"uid":5490,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"香港政府重停留係寄實體表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"成篇文就係話俾你聽個問題唔係實體表格度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地係用ocr 處理實體表<br />\n<br />\n政府請班廢人番黎處理<br />\n仲要整唔見埋"},{"pid":"e4a4063611f648830a695f456b16bd117ee39f91","tid":1768830,"uid":13663,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ottV6pm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FottV6pm.jpg&h=9c5db039&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da613d2b861e4aac904f3ffbff5d89e1b35b4d64","t